<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Earlier this month, she celebrated her 25th birthday in style, by treating herself to a luxury spa break in the Scottish Highlands.</p>

<p>And Kady McDermott kept the pampering going over the weekend, when she  shared snaps of herself enjoying a similar break at London's Glass House Retreat.</p>

<p>The former Love Island star set pulses racing as she uploaded an image of herself posing in a skimpy thong bikini – showing off her pert posterior as she posed with her back to the camera.</p>

<p>Pampered: Kady McDermott showed off her pert posterior as she shared snaps of herself enjoying a break at London's Glass House Retreat over the weekend</p>

<p>Standing before a welcoming indoor pool, the reality star opted to go makeup-free for her relaxing day, while her raven locks fell beyond her shoulders.</p>

<p>Captioning the scintillating snap, TV personality Kady simply wrote: 'Chilled weekend at the <?php echo e('@'); ?>glasshouseretreat.'</p>

<p>She also shared shots of her time at the spa, showing workout sessions, healthy vegan meals, as well as wrapping up in the comfort of a fluffy bathrobe.</p>

<p>In her element: She appeared to be in her element as she made the most of her luxury break</p>

<p>Just a tad chilly: The Love Island star shared a snap of herself going for a cryotherapy session</p>

<p>Kady recently left fans confused after she announced she is still with boyfriend Myles Barnett and they will live in their new home 'as a couple', weeks after confirming yet another 'break-up'.</p>

<p>The brunette previously took to social media to confirm she will be living in her renovated bungalow with former TOWIE star Myles, 26, when it is finished.</p>

<p>The duo bought a Hertfordshire property together in April 2019 with plans to completely transform it into a two-storey house.</p>

<p>She blamed their split on the pressure of the build which caused them to argue, as she joked that their renovation has been more stressful than having a baby.  </p>

<p>Amazing: She also revealed that she had indulged in 'the most amazing' deep tissue massage</p>

<p>Healthy delights: Among the other delights she was seen enjoying were healthy vegan meals</p>

<p>She wrote: 'Just to stop all the personal dms because we are literally get one every single minute, which is understandable.</p>

<p>'Me and Myles are will both be living in this house as a couple, couples do argue. It is a very exciting time for us both but also ridiculously stressful.</p>

<p>'Me and Myles can't wait to live in our forever home and will continue to share our journey with you.'</p>

<p>'Now I understand when people say renovating/moving home is more stressful than having a baby.' (sic)</p>

<p>Staycation! Earlier this month, the make-up artist celebrated her 25th birthday by travelling to the Scottish Highlands for a luxurious lodge break</p>

